Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.16,0:00:18.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everyone, Kaleido Star is about to start!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.13,0:00:20.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When watching Kaleido Star,\Nplease keep the room brightly lit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.87,0:00:23.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and sit as far from the TV as you can.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.07,0:00:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm Sora Naegino.\NI came to America all by myself{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.80,0:00:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}with aspirations of joining Kaleido Stage.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Everything is new to me, {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.17,0:00:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}but I'm doing my best in the spirit\Nof "try it rather than think about it."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.68,0:00:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's nothing I can't do if I try,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.93,0:00:38.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and if I can do it without\Ntrying, that'll be super lucky.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.76,0:00:41.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And if I'm gonna do it, I just\Ngotta do it! Gotta! Gotta! That's me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.68,0:00:48.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Well, well, well, what's your father like?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.38,0:00:50.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Is he nice, or is he scary? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:55.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Miss Layla's father is a workaholic\Nand he has no clue about her feelings.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.54,0:00:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even on her special birthday, he's working.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.31,0:00:59.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh! If he keeps acting that way,\NI feel sorry for Miss Layla!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.83,0:01:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I do! I do!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.05,0:01:20.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yaritai koto wa nani {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.65,0:01:23.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sou kikareru tabi {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.50,0:01:27.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Aoi sora miageta {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:31.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Kotae wa only my heart {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Honto ni daiji na kotoba\Nwa kantan ni wa iwanai{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.12,0:01:46.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hikari ga yubisasu\Nbasho e to hashiridasu yo{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Dakishimetai mono nara\Nnakitai hodo mune ni aru{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.32,0:02:01.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Egakitsuzukete yuku kitto take it someday{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.26,0:02:08.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Shiroi kumo ga nagareru\Nchiheisen no mukou ni{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.31,0:02:21.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Naranderu mirai wa itsumo soba ni aru kara{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.97,0:02:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I do a grieving\Nchimpanzee pose at the end today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.90,0:02:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.64,0:02:48.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.89,0:02:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}My chance! {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.77,0:02:52.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I should say something to make them laugh!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.42,0:02:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As you may expect from roses!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.71,0:02:56.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Roses...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:02:59.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Darn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.98,0:03:03.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I could be better at ad-libbing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.52,0:03:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That look is perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.37,0:03:08.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, that's a big bouquet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.98,0:03:10.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know. It's for Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.93,0:03:12.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her father, Mr. Hamilton, is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.96,0:03:14.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? Does he come here often?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:17.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's very busy, so he's rarely here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.87,0:03:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's the owner of Hamilton Hotels.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:22.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hamilton Hotels?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.23,0:03:23.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think we have some in Japan too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.81,0:03:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're all over the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.08,0:03:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I need to deliver this quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.65,0:03:31.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He sounds great.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.79,0:03:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"An Amazing Star Even In Tough Times."{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.60,0:03:44.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like "Cinderella"\Nwill be one of Layla's best works.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.01,0:03:45.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How is the box-office record?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.83,0:03:48.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience numbers\Nare the best in history.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.53,0:03:51.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are these three fairy godmothers?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They're newcomers who\Npassed the audition this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.45,0:03:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.35,0:03:56.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.32,0:03:57.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations on\Nthe successful production.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.75,0:04:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.95,0:04:02.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And thank you for the beautiful flowers too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.74,0:04:05.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There is no flower that\Nexceeds your beauty, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.04,0:04:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I really would like you\Nto see my show this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.43,0:04:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.81,0:04:14.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, we're having a party\Nwith top business leaders tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.94,0:04:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure you come to\Nthe party after your show.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.53,0:04:18.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.65,0:04:20.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kalos, please be her escort.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.96,0:04:22.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.81,0:04:26.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And let's invite those\Nthree fairy godmothers, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.06,0:04:27.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Those three?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.43,0:04:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's important to provide \Nthem with publicity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.22,0:04:32.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We need to have the next\Ngeneration of stars after you leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.53,0:04:35.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, I will see you tonight, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.47,0:04:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a busy person.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.95,0:04:48.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Yes. So busy that he has never\Nseen one of my shows to the end.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.79,0:04:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it perfectly again today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.60,0:04:57.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The audience seemed like they were\Nwaiting for the transformation scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.61,0:04:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it's really worth doing, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.12,0:05:01.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we stumble off the\Nstage when we exit next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.92,0:05:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.21,0:05:04.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I agree.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.53,0:05:05.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:11.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't give an unfocused performance
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.52,0:05:13.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just because you're a little popular now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.16,0:05:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.77,0:05:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But we were perfect today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.06,0:05:21.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our top star is in a bad mood.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.70,0:05:23.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's more uptight than usual
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.73,0:05:26.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,because her father's\Nhere to see her performance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.12,0:05:28.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I think he left\Nwithout watching the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.16,0:05:28.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:30.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.23,0:05:33.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All of you,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.21,0:05:35.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,go to the costume department.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.04,0:05:38.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A party?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.56,0:05:45.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's kind of awkward. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.97,0:05:48.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if I should say something?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.01,0:05:52.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was too bad that your father\Ncouldn't stay for your show today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.56,0:05:53.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.47,0:05:56.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.88,0:05:58.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is awkward. {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.08,0:06:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.20,0:06:11.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Layla Hamilton.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.95,0:06:13.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She is stunning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.46,0:06:15.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You look beautiful, Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.50,0:06:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, Father.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:20.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.62,0:06:21.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.11,0:06:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Somehow, I feel like I don't belong here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.86,0:06:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll be all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.13,0:06:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's definitely more nerve-racking\Nthan performing on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.76,0:06:33.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.80,0:06:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like they're drawing attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.83,0:06:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, do you know that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He looks familiar.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:42.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remember correctly, \Nhe's a movie producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.74,0:06:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. He's looking for\Na heroine for his next movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.25,0:06:48.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Audition for the role.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.49,0:06:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla is going to audition for a movie?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.36,0:06:55.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is a great opportunity.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.02,0:06:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To advance your career from\Nbeing Kaleido Stage's top star
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.40,0:06:59.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,to becoming a worldwide top star.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:02.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have that much commercial value.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.68,0:07:05.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.07,0:07:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.30,0:07:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:10.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw you in the newspaper.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:12.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you that fairy godmother?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.57,0:07:14.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're so cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.16,0:07:16.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, how do you do that Triple Illusion?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.62,0:07:18.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do something for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.34,0:07:21.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Please show us.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.40,0:07:22.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.78,0:07:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to do something?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.88,0:07:25.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's put on a little show.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.28,0:07:25.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, let's do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.50,0:07:28.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.16,0:07:31.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.43,0:07:34.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There, there, there, there, there, there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.95,0:07:48.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.69,0:07:51.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.16,0:07:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.76,0:07:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.45,0:08:01.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.50,0:08:06.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, well, not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.69,0:08:08.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you would come to the\Nactual stage, you could...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.51,0:08:12.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.29,0:08:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come see Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.15,0:08:16.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, for a little party joke.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.29,0:08:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ladies.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.00,0:08:20.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Miss Layla's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.27,0:08:22.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have a favor to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.57,0:08:23.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.69,0:08:26.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,To tell you the truth,\Ntomorrow is Layla's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.81,0:08:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having a party at\Nour house in the afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.43,0:08:31.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Won't you three come to the party too?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.24,0:08:32.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.36,0:08:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Definitely!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.40,0:08:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.38,0:08:36.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the day off tomorrow,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.38,0:08:39.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,please come and watch\Nour show after the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.65,0:08:42.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to work tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.58,0:08:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will make sure you get paid for your work.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.33,0:08:47.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So please be there.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.38,0:08:50.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:52.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We don't need to be paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.71,0:08:56.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll still go even if we're not paid.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:57.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You certainly are generous.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.13,0:09:00.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You will never be successful like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.56,0:09:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's awful.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.48,0:09:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's nothing new.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.91,0:09:12.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wonder if Miss Layla is lonely?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.14,0:09:26.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, I think we should brighten\Nup the mood at the party tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.13,0:09:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I'm thinking...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.97,0:09:30.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:31.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.04,0:09:37.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.61,0:09:38.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cancelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.83,0:09:40.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.43,0:09:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.88,0:09:45.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can we at least give her a present?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.09,0:09:46.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.97,0:09:49.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.10,0:09:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.28,0:09:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.83,0:09:57.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.14,0:09:57.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.51,0:10:00.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father asked you to come, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.33,0:10:01.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.05,0:10:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.03,0:10:03.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but why was it suddenly cancelled?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.11,0:10:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It wasn't sudden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:11.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Every year, my father invites\Nguests to the party by paying them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.60,0:10:13.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But a party like that is meaningless.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.68,0:10:17.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.85,0:10:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I cancel it every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.39,0:10:26.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sounds like your father doesn't\Nunderstand your feelings at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.75,0:10:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's how things work here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.37,0:10:34.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so, he cares\Nabout me in his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.30,0:10:35.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.65,0:10:38.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, haven't you heard enough?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.36,0:10:39.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.46,0:10:40.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.81,0:10:43.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I have to practice now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.08,0:10:44.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.51,0:10:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At home?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:51.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:54.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe there's a\Npractice room inside the house.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.59,0:10:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How often do you practice here, Miss Layla?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.21,0:11:01.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless I have practice for\Na new production, every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.57,0:11:03.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And on the days when my\Nperformance was unsatisfactory on stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.95,0:11:05.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That often?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.34,0:11:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your birthday today and you're still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:12.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Someday, I want my father\Nto acknowledge Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.08,0:11:17.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And for that, my performance\Nhas to be the best at all times.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.29,0:11:19.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.62,0:11:22.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The movie audition, maybe you're actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.22,0:11:23.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will audition for the movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:26.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make sure to live \Nup to his expectations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.31,0:11:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because I don't want to disappoint him.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.05,0:11:32.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you satisfied now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.92,0:11:34.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.36,0:11:36.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.22,0:11:59.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I've decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.48,0:12:01.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Decided what?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.01,0:12:16.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then after the curtain drops,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.81,0:12:19.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the curtain call will become\NMiss Layla's birthday party!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.81,0:12:21.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it sound like magic?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.57,0:12:23.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've decided \Nto do this, let's hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.90,0:12:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mia is the director.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:26.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ken and Jean are in charge of the stage sets.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.27,0:12:30.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Anna and Miss Sarah,\Nplease make the costumes.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.28,0:12:32.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Marion, you need to help us, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.06,0:12:34.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we don't have much\Ntime left before the evening show,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.53,0:12:35.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,let's get started now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.28,0:12:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.90,0:12:39.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you all doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.37,0:12:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.56,0:12:45.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Once she makes up her mind,\Nshe's the type that runs with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:47.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's one of her good traits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.33,0:12:48.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't agree more.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.46,0:12:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there any sort of trick to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.85,0:12:52.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do an adequate job, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.20,0:12:53.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.50,0:12:56.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is this? It's fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.17,0:12:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Marion!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.37,0:13:00.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.88,0:13:01.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.14,0:13:06.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder how she'll react?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.29,0:13:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.60,0:13:10.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you up to something again?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.10,0:13:13.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, we're going to celebrate\NMiss Layla's birthday.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.51,0:13:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But please keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.77,0:13:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hope everything turns out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.43,0:13:19.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.67,0:13:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:25.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Jonathan, you're going to hand the \Ncake to Miss Layla at the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.40,0:13:32.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, everything is all set to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.85,0:13:36.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, not yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.69,0:13:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Without this, it won't be magic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.91,0:13:43.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.27,0:13:44.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.27,0:13:46.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if you want it, that's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.73,0:13:48.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't contact him?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.58,0:13:50.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I can contact him, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.60,0:13:53.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.07,0:13:57.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess we can't do it after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.52,0:13:59.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.38,0:14:00.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time to sink or swim!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.66,0:14:02.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.17,0:14:04.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'll try to contact him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.46,0:14:06.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.13,0:14:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Mr. Hamilton please. Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.35,0:14:14.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She needs to talk to him \Nconcerning Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.31,0:14:18.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Sora Naegino, from Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.16,0:14:20.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well, she's still new.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:22.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not suspicious or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.53,0:14:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I am a fairy godmother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.89,0:14:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.08,0:14:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That sounds plenty suspicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.31,0:14:28.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.67,0:14:34.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mr. Hamilton, you have a phone call.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.52,0:14:36.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm in the middle of a meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.07,0:14:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.40,0:14:40.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's from someone called "fairy godmother."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.29,0:14:44.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I contact the police?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.05,0:14:45.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll take it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry to call you at work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.48,0:14:50.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what business does a\Nfairy godmother have with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.57,0:14:53.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you want to get\Npaid for the party after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:54.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The party was cancelled.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:55.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.33,0:14:56.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has been cancelled every year.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.27,0:14:59.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla was practicing by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.83,0:15:01.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.17,0:15:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're having a birthday\Nparty for her at Kaleido Stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.25,0:15:09.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And we would very much\Nlike you to attend the party.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.63,0:15:11.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.11,0:15:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's impossible, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.54,0:15:15.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, I want you to\Nsee Miss Layla's show, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.39,0:15:19.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It takes four hours from here\Nto Cape Mary even by private jet.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.52,0:15:21.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I won't make it in time\Nfor the start of the show.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:23.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then at least, can you make it\Nto the end of the show? Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.25,0:15:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you for letting me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.77,0:15:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to you, I now know how Layla feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.19,0:15:32.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like she wasn't happy\Nwith a party that I bought for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.86,0:15:35.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:35.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.70,0:15:39.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't understand how Miss Layla feels.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:43.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It doesn't matter how many people are there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.11,0:15:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the person she wants\Nmost to be there doesn't come,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,she'll just feel even more alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.15,0:15:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She feels lonely and sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.60,0:15:54.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's why she cancels the\Nparties and just practices by herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She needs her father.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.87,0:15:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please come.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.42,0:16:05.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Inviting Miss Layla's father?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.67,0:16:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. It seems Sora is calling him right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.02,0:16:09.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.29,0:16:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You never know, because it's Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.52,0:16:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.19,0:16:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse us.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.86,0:16:16.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.80,0:16:21.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla, your father's like,\Ncoming to see your show.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.38,0:16:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My father? There is no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But today's your birthday, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.92,0:17:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.18,0:17:49.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.19,0:17:55.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Miss Layla!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.99,0:17:57.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is from all of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.36,0:18:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A small...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.64,0:18:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,present.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.27,0:18:08.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.80,0:18:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.60,0:18:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! It was a big success!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.47,0:18:50.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We did it, Sora!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.76,0:18:52.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.36,0:18:53.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla seemed happy with...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.06,0:18:57.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is the meaning of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.39,0:18:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you come up with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.39,0:19:01.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.18,0:19:03.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop doing things like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never appeared so dumbstruck\Nin front of an audience before.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.20,0:19:10.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh... I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.35,0:19:13.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't do anything like this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.64,0:19:17.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.48,0:19:18.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.36,0:19:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You still have something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.68,0:19:21.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,At the very least, please take this cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.78,0:19:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, the cake isn't really that important,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.19,0:19:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but there's a message.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.53,0:19:29.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got this message personally \Nfrom your father.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.14,0:19:30.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.00,0:19:32.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.75,0:19:38.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought everything turned out fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.15,0:19:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be discouraged, Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.20,0:19:41.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.98,0:19:43.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.38,0:19:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. It was like, \Nunnecessary after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.09,0:20:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got this message personally \Nfrom your father.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.33,0:20:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Please don't do anything like this again.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.06,0:20:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why am I so irritated? {\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.47,0:20:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Happy birthday, Miss Layla.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.47,0:20:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's because I pushed for the birthday party.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.79,0:20:40.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, we were all in on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.08,0:20:42.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Miss Layla doesn't\Nlike that sort of thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.12,0:20:47.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In the end, I ignored Miss Layla's feelings
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.08,0:20:49.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,just like her father did.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.57,0:20:51.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do with that cake?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.18,0:20:52.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You want to eat it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.34,0:20:54.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, we did take the time to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.86,0:20:55.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.68,0:21:01.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to at least\Ndeliver the message to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.09,0:21:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.04,0:21:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She may get mad at you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.03,0:21:06.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'm already used to\Nsomeone being mad at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sora, I'm coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.91,0:21:10.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Please do!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.10,0:21:12.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, here it is! Here it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.93,0:21:14.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.81,0:21:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.37,0:21:20.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Miss Layla's maid just \Ncame to pick up the cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.42,0:21:21.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.28,0:21:24.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,She said she'll at least accept the\Ncake since you took the time to make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.22,0:21:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Really! Layla can be so \Npretentious sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.63,0:21:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I will leave the cake here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.72,0:21:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
